{"tid":1723394,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好咁快屌段崇智住啦","createTime":"2019-11-15T07:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T14:08:57.000Z","uid":44925,"like":58,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"52cf787bc97a63ca19d932b393fdb7308d807446","tid":1723394,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:30:12.000Z","msg":"其實佢可以做既野根本唔多<br />\nUGC既校長講到底其實就係政府打工仔<br />\n香港政府黑警大陸官媒開恆火屌柒佢 佢做得d乜<br />\n你就算屌柒佢都無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實果日佢未落黎果陣佢係office一直同政府deal緊<br />\n就算親身落到黎都要俾黑警tg射走<br />\n加上其實好多人現場一見佢係屌佢老母 連記者都唔俾面佢對佢態度勁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對一個咁高地位既學者其實係屈辱 佢EQ已經算好高架啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢而家未報警 未篤灰 就算啦 <br />\n封公開信可以唔駛理<br />\n而且吳副校長真係好關心學生<br />\n<br />\n大家請冷靜d 針對返班更仆街既人<br />\n<br />\n真係要裝修 搞掂左Shitty同Poly兩個仆街先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca1fc95efd63f148514a0dd17abf3a4d5ad654b","tid":1723394,"uid":120627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:33:23.000Z","msg":"［注意］請勿跌入林鄭分化圈套［注意］<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1723355\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1723355</a>"},{"pid":"4f5c21472ee7b3f1bde71160abf3c2e60e301b26","tid":1723394,"uid":44925,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:33:44.000Z","msg":"比起張狗 郭狗 藤狗<br />\n段王爺已經算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a808febe1350dd3b3a631972dd284f3b1822da6","tid":1723394,"uid":196812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9db58806586f80103cdb03de8029926d519c22","tid":1723394,"uid":44925,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:36:46.000Z","msg":"而且佢拋波俾非CU人<br />\n某程度上係保緊中大學生<br />\n<br />\n大家諗下先"},{"pid":"0e020235b0ce3d8ff8a484